STEPS for testing 

Step 1 - Make changes to Spidermon 
Step 2 - Build the package by recompiling Spidermon again correctly through this command. 

python setup.py sdist bdist_dumb

When built, shift it to Spider-tutorial for testing 

Step 3 - Activate virtualenv
Step 4 - Install the new Spidermon, pip install package_name

It should now go on to be installed without a hitch. 

Step 5 : TEST 